  "title": "Site Coordinator (Cable Laying | Pavement Certification)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2500 to $4000 + Allowances + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Joo Koon</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Normal working hours</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Cable Laying Experience with Pavement Cert will be advantage</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Lead &amp; oversee the planning, scheduling, and execution of cable laying projects</strong> from start to finish, ensuring adherence to timelines, quality standards, and budget constraints.</li>\n  <li>Provide regular progress reports to stakeholders, highlighting key developments, risks, and mitigation strategies.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with engineering teams to <strong>ensure proper installation and handling of cables installations.</strong></li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with all safety protocols, including cable protection, trenching, and traffic management.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with external contractors, vendors, and suppliers to ensure the timely delivery of necessary materials and equipment.</li>\n  <li>Act as the primary point of contact for any project-related issues, troubleshooting problems as they arise.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular site inspections to monitor the progress and quality of cable laying works.</li>\n  <li>Lead and mentor junior coordinators and site teams, providing guidance and technical expertise where needed.</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned by management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate have <strong>cable laying experience with pavement certificate</strong> will be an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG JYA YEE (R23119014)<br>\nEA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br>\nEA License No: 21C0492</p>",
